Feature: Deposit Page
As a User
I want to deposit amount
So that I can have an increased total deposit

Scenario: User successfully deposited
Given I am on the deposit page
Then I should see "Phone Number"
And I should see "ID number"
And I should see "New Deposit"
And I should see "Enter" button
When I fill in "Phone Number" with "070000000000" 
And I fill in "ID Number" with "12345678"
And I fill in "New Deposit" with "1234"
And I click Enter
Then I shoud be redirect to show page
And I should see "Phone Number: 070000000000"
And I should see "ID Number: 12345678"
And I should see "New Deposit: 1234"
And I should see "Balance: 1234"